high_descs: Take the sweet potato out of the microwave.
Turn right and walk up to the fridge.
Put the sweet potato in the fridge and close the door, after a couple seconds open the door and remove the now chilled sweet potato, then close the door.
Turn left and walk back over to the microwave.
Put the chilled sweet potato in the microwave to the right of the apple then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled sweet potato in the microwave.

high_descs: open microwave, pick up potato from microwave, close microwave
go to refrigerator to the right
open refrigerator, place potato to the right of tomato on second shelf of refrigerator, close refrigerator, open refrigerator, pick up potato from refrigerator, close refrigerator
go to counter with microwave to the left
place potato on center of blue plate in microwave, close microwave
anns.task_desc: Place chilled potato on blue plate in microwave

high_descs: Walk forward to the microwave in front of you.
Take out the potato from the microwave and close the microwave.
Turn right and walk to the refrigerator.
Cool the potato in the refrigerator, then take it out and close the refrigerator.
Turn left and walk back to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave and close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled potato in a microwave.
